name: Corporate Design Solutions
overview:
Based in Buderim on the beautiful Sunshine Coast, Queensland, Corporate Design Solutions creates award winning print, graphic design, web design and web site development solutions. We are a creative agency who undertakes strategic and creative thinking to get our clients to where they want to go, and beyond.

Our company specialises in corporate web design, professional logo design, graphic design, signage solutions and print management for all types of businesses and industries in Queensland and across the eastern seaboard of Australia.

We understand that first impressions are crucial to the success of any business and that this professional image must be maintained through consistent branding. Your logo, stationery, web design and other marketing materials must portray your business in a manner that can be easily transfered to many types of promotional marketing with ease.

We take the headache out of design by providing a complete design service with a personal, friendly approach. To compliment our full design service, we give our clients the option of allowing us to take care of all your printing requirements at reduced trade rates.
